trans-unit.source: Encapsulates a collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> instances and is used for properties whose <xref:System.Type> is a collection.
trans-unit.target: Innkapsler en samling av <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> forekomster og er brukt for egenskaper som har egenskapen <xref:System.Type>er en samling.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueCollection"></xref> class as a sub-property to the specified parent <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueCollection"> </xref> klassen som en undertype egenskap til den angitte overordnet <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The parent <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Overordnet <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Adds an object into the collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Legger til et objekt i samlingen av <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The object to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Objektet til å legge til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> for the added object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> for objektet som er lagt til.

trans-unit.source: Notifies listeners of dynamic changes to the collection, such as when items get added and removed or the whole list is refreshed.
trans-unit.target: Varsler lyttere om dynamisk endringer i samlingen, for eksempel når elementer få legges til og fjernes eller hele listen oppdateres.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of items in a collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Henter antallet elementer i en samling av <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Int32> number of items.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Int32>antall elementer.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Returns a strongly typed <xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator> that iterates through the collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en forespørselsparameter av sterk type <xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator>som går gjennom samlingen av <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> objekter.</xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601> object that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601> objekt som kan brukes til å gå gjennom samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Inserts a specified object at the specified index in a collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Setter inn et objekt som er angitt i den angitte indeksen i en samling av <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The object to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Objektet til å legge til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The index number that specifies where to insert the object into the collection.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen tall som angir hvor man kan sette inn objektet i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> for the added object.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> for objektet som er lagt til.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> from a collection at the given index.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> fra en samling i den angitte indeksen.

trans-unit.source: The index of the item to be returned.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for elementet som skal returneres.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> at that index.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> på indeksen.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueCollection.CollectionChanged"></xref> event when items in the collection are added, removed, or resorted.
trans-unit.target: Hever den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueCollection.CollectionChanged"> </xref> -hendelse når legges til, fjerne eller resorted elementer i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Event arguments that contain information about the change in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Hendelsen argumenter som inneholder informasjon om endringen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the parent <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> object that contains the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter overordnet <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> objekt som inneholder samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> of the parent.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> for overordnede.

trans-unit.source: Removes the object from the collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner objektet fra samlingen av <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The host needs to ensure that the PropertyValue is invalid after the object is removed.
trans-unit.target: Verten må kontrollere at PropertyValue er ugyldig når objektet er fjernet.

trans-unit.source: The item to remove from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Elementet som skal fjernes fra samlingen.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if removal is successful; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis fjerningen er fullført. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Removes the object from the collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> objects at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner objektet fra samlingen av <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> objekter i den angitte indeksen.

trans-unit.source: The index of the item to remove.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for elementet som skal fjernes.

trans-unit.source: Recalculates the indexes in a collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> objects after an existing item is moved to a new position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Beregner på nytt indekser i en samling av <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> objekter etter et eksisterende element er flyttet til en ny plassering i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The current position index of the object in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Gjeldende posisjon indeksen for objektet i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The index position to which the item is moved.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen posisjonen som elementet er flyttet.

trans-unit.source: Returns a strongly typed <xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator> for a collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en forespørselsparameter av sterk type <xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator>for en samling av <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> objekter.</xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> object that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>objekt som kan brukes til å gå gjennom samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>
